query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('antlr4',
'cell',
'cordova-plugins',
'database-trigger',
'derby',
'domain-driven-design',
'exchange-server',
'google-maps-markers',
'ios9',
'maven-plugin',
'seaborn',
'xml-serialization');
